recipe.title: Jalapeno Cornbread Stuffing
recipe.summary: Jalapeno Cornbread Stuffing takes approximately 45 minutes from beginning to end. For $1.86 per serving, you get a side dish that serves 10. One serving contains 728 calories, 14g of protein, and 28g of fat. 9 people were impressed by this recipe. Head to the store and pick up salt, onion, celery, and a few other things to make it today. Only a few people really liked this Southern dish. It will be a hit at your Thanksgiving event. It is a good option if you're following a lacto ovo vegetarian diet. It is brought to you by Foodista. With a spoonacular score of 33%, this dish is not so super. Similar recipes include Cornbread Stuffing, Cornbread for Stuffing, and Cornbread Stuffing.
